As we head into the new season, here is Team 2539’s code for the 2024 season! Although it has always been public, I just thought it would be good to make it accessible through Chief Delphi.

github.com

GitHub - FRC2539/javabot-2024: Team 2539's robot code for the 2024 season:...

Team 2539's robot code for the 2024 season: Crescendo.

General structure wise we are Java command based and use the CTRE Swerve Generator. We use Limelight for vision and PathPlanner for autos.

If you have any questions, feel free to ask them!
